Primary Objective: To study the effect of mild, moderate, and severe renal impairment on the pharmacokinetics (PK) of eliglustat.

 Secondary Objective: To assess the tolerability of eliglustat tartrate given as a single dose in subjects with mild, moderate, and severe renal impairment in comparison with matched subjects with normal renal function.

